      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely stunning and in truly flawless condition. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, kept meticulously clean and always garaged. It honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
