    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest possible standard and presenting in showroom-fresh condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather seats still retain their factory scent and firm support, with no signs of wear, creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been garage-kept and serviced exclusively at certified dealerships with a full paper trail of preventative maintenance. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or debris. If you are looking for a vehicle that feels as though it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
